    <p>These cookies track your activity to deliver relevant advertisements and measure ad campaign effectiveness.</p>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Cookie Name</th>
        <th>Purpose</th>
        <th>Duration</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>_fbp</td>
