        <td>3 months</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>ads_prefs</td>
        <td>Advertising preferences</td>
        <td>1 year</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>How to Manage Cookies</h2>
    <p>You have several options for managing cookies:</p>

    <h3>Cookie Banner</h3>
    <p>When you first visit GetPawsy, you'll see a cookie consent banner. You can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Accept All:</strong> Enable all cookies for the full experience</li>
      <li><strong>Essential Only:</strong> Only necessary cookies will be used</li>
      <li><strong>Customize:</strong> Choose which cookie categories to enable</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Browser Settings</h3>
    <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings > Privacy and Security > Cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Options > Privacy & Security > Cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences > Privacy > Cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings > Privacy & Security > Cookies</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Opt-Out Links</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank">Google Analytics Opt-Out</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/settings/?tab=ads" target="_blank">Facebook Ad Preferences</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>
    <p>If you disable cookies, some features may not work properly:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Shopping cart may not save items</li>
      <li>You may need to log in repeatedly</li>
      <li>Product recommendations may be less relevant</li>
      <li>Site preferences won't be remembered</li>
      <li>Checkout process may be affected</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p>Some cookies are set by third-party services we use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> Stripe, PayPal for secure payments</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics for site improvement</li>
      <li><strong>Social Media:</strong> Facebook, Instagram for social features</li>
      <li><strong>AI Services:</strong> For chatbot and recommendation functionality</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These third parties have their own privacy policies governing their use of cookies.</p>

    <h2>Cookie Lifespan</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
      <li><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain for a specified period (see tables above)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Questions about our use of cookies?</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: privacy@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li>Visit: <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a></li>
    </ul>
  </main>

